reviewText: Would have liked to known that the last half of the directors cut of payback was an alternate ending totally different from the released version.
For some reason only one film: 'We were soldiers', would not play on My detachable PC, DVD player. Hmmm. Excellent films for an excellent price, overall very happy, thanks much!
A nice variety for the different movie watching moods.
Payback is a Director's cut and not the theater version.  I did not like this version as much as the original.
Plays great. Mel Gibson is a good actor. These are some of his best.
